  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is the evaluation of the frequency of xerostomia and their management
      after radiotherapy in head and neck cancer.

      The quality of life of these patients is also analysed with European Organization for
      Research and Treatment of Cancer Quality of life Questionnaire H&amp;N35 (EORTC QLQ H&amp;N35).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
